Name: E-Ball
About the game: E-ball is a quick twitch isometric platform game that will put a players thumb skills to the test. Guide your E-ball towards the finish line while collecting valuable orbs and beating the clock. Race through 4 zones and 20 stages of palm sweating challenges from spiked pits of doom to fire spitting totems!
